{"tid":2491008,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]唔知飛鹿洗唔洗交稅?","createTime":"2021-04-16T04:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:45:20.000Z","uid":110851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1be6b490de5c1be397268dd86e0ed32c39f3b24e","tid":2491008,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"例如飛鹿同代理拎3070 來貨價$7000<br />\n但係飛鹿處處為客著想<br />\n為咗令大家買到原價顯示卡 竟然用NVIDIA建議零售價499USD(~$4000)賣畀harryw<br />\n公司每賣一張3070就蝕$3000 搞手今次連和都打唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於harryw拎啲卡去二手市場(dc fever)炒賣 飛馬控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛鹿一個月賣十張3070蝕3皮 harryw就賺到盆滿缽滿<br />\n有限公司蝕錢好似唔洗交稅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊聞: 廉署控2店員 非法售iPhone 4<br />\n<a href=\"https://paper.hket.com/article/743560/%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E6%8E%A72%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%20%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%94%AEiPhone%204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F743560%2F%25E5%25BB%2589%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258E%25A72%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%2593%25A1%2520%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2594%25AEiPhone%25204&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLRmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=6fb11730\" target=\"_blank\">https://paper.hket.com/article/743560/%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E6%8E%A72%E5%BA%97%E5%93%A1%20%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E5%94%AEiPhone%204</a><br />\n員工扣起iphone自己炒會畀人拉 老細咁做應該冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映: 飛馬處處為客著想 幫大陸客拎貨上深圳再寄順豐 幫個客慳唔少稅<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY5fRBA3Je2puUo9iT66PjcyJt4CECeQNgtv4MVJt9tTf?filename=vzF1Ker.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzF1Ker.jpg&h=6fd97e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講飛馬個老細商科出身 應該會識答有限公司蝕錢洗唔洗交稅哩個問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日有間mark i又係用飛馬電話 唔知關唔關事?<br />\n<br />\n開咗間網店俾人當咗係飛馬附屬公司  你問我盡量答<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2486978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2486978</a><br />\n<br />\n啲錢洗下就會變返乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飛馬潛咗幾日水會唔會係搞返啲手尾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住賠返$1000畀讓治巴打 撳返低件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42304002b2565ea506229263a3fd96007af02502","tid":2491008,"uid":49532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"腦場文化呀 你班外行人兒登仔識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e715738ca8d901e275c3d8d7eb886e76035b69a1","tid":2491008,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42304002b2565ea506229263a3fd96007af02502","tid":2491008,"uid":49532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"腦場文化呀 你班外行人兒登仔識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"文化差異可以解釋世界上所有問題"},{"pid":"958b1cc10d6532dd33410cfd01023ece58f59b8f","tid":2491008,"uid":373119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"即係走馬公司7000 拎貨<br />\n4000 賣俾自己人炒貨 13000 蚊一張再私下分錢？<br />\n避稅又賺多一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 唔識腦場文化"},{"pid":"a07606ccd1856a7eb9c01d34dc16dc1b99460c4c","tid":2491008,"uid":110851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42304002b2565ea506229263a3fd96007af02502","tid":2491008,"uid":49532,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-