>\n節錄: <br />\n為興趣棄高薪厚職<br />\n余卓羲今年只得 26 歲，2 年前甫大學畢業即開始創業，成立飛馬電腦，業務主要是代客「砌機」 (組裝電腦) 。<span class=\"red\">余卓羲雖主修商科</span>，但一直對資訊科技素有興趣，大學時期更自修數個電腦課程並獲 IBM 聘請為實習生，月入2 萬元的職位只要「轉正」，3 萬多元的月薪就是唾手可得。惟當時職務擔任部門與部門聯絡，跟余卓羲喜歡於前線打拼的興趣不符，遂毅然創業。<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://sme.hket.com/article/2447340/90%E5%BE%8C%E6%A3%84%E9%AB%98%E8%96%AA%E5%8E%9A%E8%81%B7%20%E7%A0%8C%E6%A9%9F%E7%A0%8C%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsme.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2447340%2F90%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25A3%2584%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2596%25AA%25E5%258E%259A%25E8%2581%25B7%2520%25E7%25A0%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25A0%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259C%25B0&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLRmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=9475ed38\" target=\"_blank\">https://sme.hket.com/article/2447340/90%E5%BE%8C%E6%A3%84%E9%AB%98%E8%96%AA%E5%8E%9A%E8%81%B7%20%E7%A0%8C%E6%A9%9F%E7%A0%8C%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%A4%A9%E5%9C%B0</a>"},{"pid":"0c60434ca46d8713c66f7273c42c110a6eaa4c0d","tid":2491008,"uid":217028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:41:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1cf98fe1e5528815b8356848f61a4e8573dc6828","tid":2491008,"uid":110851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"收$1000訂就排得隊買顯示卡<br />\n大家排咁耐都未到 其實係harryw排第一<br />\n佢落$1000訂100張顯示卡 其他人慢慢等啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd5c04101ab3fc63d94376edb7fbe584ffaf94b","tid":2491008,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cf98fe1e5528815b8356848f61a4e8573dc6828","tid":2491008,"uid":110851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"收$1000訂就排得隊買顯示卡<br />\n大家排咁耐都未到 其實係harryw排第一<br />\n佢落$1000訂100張顯示卡 其他人慢慢等啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n